parameters.name: Bucket
parameters.description: The name of the logical Object Storage Service (OSS) bucket.

parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The end of the time range to query. The time is in UTC. Format: 2010-01-21T09:50:23Z.

parameters.name: Period
parameters.description:
The aggregation granularity. Unit: minutes.

Default value: 5. Valid values: 5 to 1440.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. The time is in UTC. Format: 2010-01-21T09:50:23Z.
